USAGE

	> Following commands were tested on [Ubuntu] 25.10 [Linux].

	1) Install [rustup]:

		$ curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh

	2) Build [bullpipe]:

		$ cargo build --release

	3) Install [espflash]:

		$ cargo install --locked espflash@=4.2

	4) Flash [bullpipe]:

		$ cargo run --release

CONTRIBUTING

	> Following commands were tested on [Ubuntu] 25.10 [Linux].

	1) Follow steps in %USAGE% section.

	2) Install [rust-analyzer] and [clippy]:

		$ rustup component add rust-analyzer clippy

